<a name="skipmaincontent"></a><h1 class="bac">Global Middle Office</h1>
<h2 class="bac">Our Business</h2>
<p class="bac">

The Middle Office focus is to provide control discipline around the accuracy, completeness and timing of all data elements used in the quantification of risk, profit and loss and financial reporting. 
</p>
<p class="bac">
Overseeing the collation and dissemination of data to multiple business partners, the Middle Office is uniquely positioned to support the Global Markets Group’s business goals.
</p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

<h2 class="bac">Overview</h2>
<p class="bac">
Global Middle Office offers interns the opportunity to work with teams helping to design workflows for new products and develop and implement automation solutions to capture processing efficiencies. Interns work closely with partners across multiple businesses, including our profit & loss, finance, compliance, risk, technology and front office teams. 
</p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

<h2 class="bac">Qualifications</h2>

<p class="bac">
Candidates must demonstrate a combination of academic aptitude, quantitative skills, strategic and creative thinking and written and oral communications skills.  In addition you must be realistically expecting to obtain a minimum 2:1 degree or equivalent.  Underlying all this, you must demonstrate dedication to a career in Middle Office. 
</p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

<h2 class="bac">Training</h2>

<p class="bac">
Bank of America’s summer analyst programme is the ideal opportunity to gain an introduction into the world of middle Office. The 10-week programme kicks off with an induction week covering core skills before you hit your desk where you will work along side our fulltime associates.  Throughout the summer, as well as receiving support from your line manager, HR and a buddy, you will also experience a number of social and educational events giving you a great insight into Bank of America. If you perform well over the summer, you may go back to university with a job offer for the following year enabling you to truly focus on your studies.
</p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

<h2 class="bac">Locations</h2>

<p class="bac">
Analysts will be placed in one of our three London sites, based in Canary Wharf, Croydon or Bromley. 
</p>



